{"tid":903083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經民聯林健鋒批評美國會報告「唯恐天下不亂」損人不利己　","createTime":"2018-11-15T09:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T12:08:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"24634ef28b7b5cad4733550b04b012cea3a04f2a","tid":903083,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:39:45.000Z","msg":"美國國會「美中經濟與安全審議委員會」發表報告，建議商務部等政府機構，檢視軍民兩用技術出口管制政策中，把香港與中國大陸視為兩個不同關稅區的做法是否合適。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員林健鋒表示，中美貿易戰對港商的影響逐漸浮現，有關建議更是火上加油、「唯恐天下不亂」和損人不利己。<br />\n<br />\n對於報告指香港言論和集會自由受到持續增加的挑戰，林健鋒表示不同意，重申本港自回歸起，依法落實一國兩制，容許公民享有自由。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄表示，有關報告是搬弄是非，抹黑香港實際情況，有關措施更是想全面壓制中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428502-20181115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428502-20181115.htm&d=XciyCYDR5ar%2FqBRqMlYw954f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=05f3844d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1428502-20181115.htm&h=ade0af94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1428502-20181115.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ca6a6abc35eb4886d4c15f552eae01b57df20e6","tid":903083,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:45:52.000Z","msg":"香港反擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9730b593d5e9681beeeb7b6deabf34061e90dfc6","tid":903083,"uid":4783,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"關你班賤種撚事<br />\n連你去美國visa都cancel埋就搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f798070dbbae30cce01e6cfecfebc4551bbc1cd2","tid":903083,"uid":50457,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"香港，愈亂愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299b236e48d40125d7d34fb2ca887c0cd65e9a56","tid":903083,"uid":192778,"like"